Package: flint
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libc6, libcurl4 | libcurl3, clang | gcc
Description: Pipeline-oriented systems programming language
 Flint is a statically-typed, pipeline-oriented language that transpiles
 to C99. Designed as a modern, dependency-free replacement for Bash and
 Python in DevOps and CLI automation contexts.
 .
 Features include:
  * Linear data flow via pipeline operator (~>)
  * Strict Type Checker with Rust-style contextual diagnostics
  * Zero-copy string manipulation and mmap-based I/O
  * Universal bracket indexing for Arrays, Structs, and JSON
  * Smart error recovery and explicit intercept blocks (catch)
 .
 Homepage: https://github.com/lucaas-d3v/flint